# Joint-fix acceptance baselines

Screenshots captured by `tests/e2e/musicians-joint-fix-acceptance.spec.ts`
land under this directory, one subdirectory per phase:

- `before/` — broken-prod baseline (Phase 0)
- `A1/` — after rail-containment fix (Stream A)
- `A2/` — after graph-viewport fix (Stream A)
- `B3/` — after era-strip data wiring (Stream B)
- `integration/` — after integration check (both streams merged)

The plan for the joint fix lives at `apps/musicians/docs/plans/2026-05-19-joint-crit-fix.md`.
The root-cause analyses live at `apps/musicians/docs/diagnostics/`.
